{"word":"ἐοικότως","slug":"ἐοικότως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐοικότως</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Adverb'>Adv.</a> of <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>ἐοικώς</el>,\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>similarly, like</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>reasonably, fairly, naturally</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>οὐκ εἰκότως</el> un<i>fairly</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}